Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation=‘And Ye Shall Be as Gods’
  - 670
By: Jâmî
Format: verse
---
Philosophers devoid of reason find
This world a mere idea of the mind;
  ’Tis an idea—but they fail to see
The great Idealist who looms behind
